-- Raiffeisen’s Ukrainian Unit Sees No Rise in Credit Portfolio
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-04-20T13:04:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-20/raiffeisen-s-ukrainian-unit-sees-no-rise-in-credit-portfolio-1-.html
Raiffeisen Bank International AG (RBI) ’s
Ukrainian unit, Aval, doesn’t expect its credit portfolio to
rise this year, the unit’s Chief Executive Officer Volodymyr
Lavrenchuk told reporters today in Kiev.  The unit also doesn’t need to raise capital this year
because of a lack of demand, and there are no macroeconomic
reasons for the hrvynia’s devaluation, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
